org.semanticweb.owlapi.profiles

Class OWL2Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.owlapi.profiles.OWL2Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasIRI, OWLProfile

    public class OWL2Profile
extends Object
implements OWLProfile
    Checks to see if an ontology and its imports closure fall into the OWL 2 DL profile. An ontology is OWL Full if any of the global structural restrictions are violated, if there is punning between object and data properties.
    Author:
    Matthew Horridge, The University Of Manchester, Information Management Group, Date: 21-Jun-2008
